Package: pestim
Type: Package
Title: Population Estimations Using Mobile Phone Data
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2018-02-01
Authors@R: c(person("David", "Salgado", email = "david.Salgado.fernandez@gmail.com", 
    role = c("aut")), 
    person("Bogdan", "Oancea", email = "bogdan.oancea@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "ctb", "cre")))
Description: This package contains functions that implement a simple
    hierarchical model to estimate the population counts of different territorial
    cells combining the information from aggregated mobile phone data and a
    population register or survey data.
